KET_LISTENING_UNITS = [{'name': '听力基础', 'description': 'KET听力考试的题型分析和基础训练', 'sort_order': 1, 'lessons': [{'title': 'KET听力概述', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': 'KET听力有5个部分，总时长约30分钟。这节课我们来了解题型和基本策略。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': 'KET听力题型', 'content': 'Part 1: 选择题 — 听3段短对话，选正确的图片（共6题）\nPart 2: 填空题 — 听一段对话，填写缺失信息\nPart 3: 选择题 — 听一段对话，回答选择题\nPart 4: 选择题 — 听一段较长的对话或独白\nPart 5: 匹配题 — 听5段短对话，匹配主题'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '听力Part 1例题：听到 "What\'s your favorite subject?" "I really enjoy art class."', 'solution': '关键词：favorite subject, art class\n答案：选择与"art"或"画画"相关的图片\n技巧：听关键词，不用每句都听懂'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '听力Part 2例题：听到 "The meeting is at 3 o\'clock in Room 201."', 'solution': "填空：The meeting is at ___ in Room ___.\n答案：3 o'clock, 201\n技巧：提前读题，注意听数字和时间"}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '听到 "I usually have lunch at twelve thirty." What time does the person have lunch?', 'options': ['12:30', '12:00', '1:30', '11:30'], 'answer': '12:30'}, {'question': '听到 "The bus leaves from Gate 5." Which gate?', 'options': ['5', '15', '50', 'Gate'], 'answer': '5'}, {'question': '听到 "She bought three tickets for the concert." How many tickets?', 'options': ['3', '2', '4', '1'], 'answer': '3'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '听力策略：提前读题→听关键词→注意数字和时间→不要纠结没听清的词。'}]}}, {'title': '数字与时间听辨', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '数字和时间是KET听力必考内容。掌握英式数字表达和时间的读法非常重要。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '数字和时间表达', 'content': '时间：7:15 = quarter past seven / seven fifteen\n7:45 = quarter to eight / seven forty-five\n7:30 = half past seven\n价格：£2.50 = two pounds fifty\n$15.99 = fifteen dollars ninety-nine cents\n电话号码：读每个数字 555-1234 = five five five one two three four\n日期：March 15th = March the fifteenth'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '听到 "The train leaves at half past nine in the morning."', 'solution': '时间 = 9:30 AM\nhalf past = 30分，nine = 9点'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '听到 "The ticket costs twelve pounds fifty."', 'solution': '价格 = £12.50\ntwelve pounds fifty = 12镑50便士'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '听到 "quarter to three"，时间是？', 'options': ['2:45', '3:15', '3:45', '2:15'], 'answer': '2:45'}, {'question': '听到 "five hundred and twenty-three"，数字是？', 'options': ['523', '503', '532', '525'], 'answer': '523'}, {'question': '听到 "double seven zero one"，号码是？', 'options': ['7701', '7711', '7017', '7770'], 'answer': '7701'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '数字听辨：quarter past/to, half past, double。听到数字立即记下来，注意区分-ty和-teen。'}]}}, {'title': '地点与方向听辨', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': 'KET听力常考地点和方向。掌握相关词汇和听辨技巧。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '地点听力关键词', 'content': 'post office, bank, hospital, school, library, museum\nsupermarket, restaurant, cafe, cinema, theater\nstation, airport, hotel, park, beach\n方位词：left, right, straight ahead, opposite, next to\nbetween, behind, in front of, near, corner'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '听到 "Go straight ahead, then turn left at the traffic lights. The bank is on your right."', 'solution': '路线：直行→红绿灯左转→右边是银行\n答案：The bank is on the right after turning left.'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '听到 "The library is opposite the supermarket, between the school and the hospital."', 'solution': '位置：图书馆在超市对面，在学校和医院之间。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '听到 "Turn right at the corner. The cafe is next to the bookstore." Where is the cafe?', 'options': ['Next to the bookstore', 'At the corner', 'Opposite the bookstore', 'Behind the corner'], 'answer': 'Next to the bookstore'}, {'question': '听到 "The school is behind the park." Where is the school?', 'options': ['Behind the park', 'In front of the park', 'Next to the park', 'Inside the park'], 'answer': 'Behind the park'}, {'question': '听到 "Go past the hospital and it\'s on your left." What do you pass first?', 'options': ['The hospital', 'The destination', 'A park', 'A school'], 'answer': 'The hospital'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '地点听力：注意方位词序列，画出路线图。听到first/second/third注意顺序。'}]}}, {'title': '听力综合练习', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '综合练习巩固听力技巧，涵盖数字、时间、地点和关键信息。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '综合听力策略', 'content': '① 听前：快速读题，标注关键词\n② 听时：专注关键信息，记笔记\n③ 听后：根据记忆和笔记选答案\n④ 不要留空——猜测也比空着好\n⑤ 利用第二次播放验证答案'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '综合练习：听到一段对话，两人讨论周末计划', 'solution': "Tom: What are you doing this weekend, Sarah?\nSarah: I'm going shopping on Saturday. I need to buy a present for my mom.\nTom: That's nice. What about Sunday?\nSarah: I'll probably stay home and study.\n问题：What is Sarah doing on Saturday? Answer: Going shopping."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '综合练习：听到一段电话留言', 'solution': 'Hi, this is a message for Mr. Brown. Your appointment on Thursday at 2:30 PM has been changed to Friday at 3:00 PM. Please call us to confirm. Thank you.\n问题：When is the new appointment? Answer: Friday at 3:00 PM.'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '听到 "The library is open from 9am to 5pm on weekdays." When is the library closed?', 'options': ['Weekends', 'Monday', 'Wednesday', 'Never'], 'answer': 'Weekends'}, {'question': '听到 "I\'d like two tickets for the 7pm show, please." What time is the show?', 'options': ['7pm', '2pm', '5pm', '9pm'], 'answer': '7pm'}, {'question': '听到 "The bus to the airport takes about 45 minutes." How long is the bus ride?', 'options': ['45 minutes', '40 minutes', '50 minutes', '15 minutes'], 'answer': '45 minutes'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '听力综合：预读题目→专注关键词→记笔记→利用第二遍验证。不纠结生词！'}]}}]}, {'name': '对话理解', 'description': '训练听懂日常对话的能力', 'sort_order': 2, 'lessons': [{'title': '购物对话', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '购物是KET听力高频话题。掌握购物相关表达和对话模式。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '购物常用表达', 'content': "Can I help you? / I'm looking for...\nHow much is this? / It's $...\nCan I try it on? / What size do you need?\nI'll take it. / Do you have anything cheaper?\nWould you like a bag? / How would you like to pay?\nCash or card? / Here's your receipt."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "购物对话：\nA: Can I help you?\nB: Yes, I'm looking for a blue jacket, size M.\nA: Here you are. It's $45.\nB: Can I try it on?\nA: Sure, the fitting room is over there.\nB: It fits perfectly. I'll take it.", 'solution': '关键信息：蓝色夹克，M号，$45，买了。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "购物对话：\nA: How much are these shoes?\nB: They're $80, but we have a 20% discount today.\nA: Great! I'll take them.\nB: That's $64. How would you like to pay?\nA: By card, please.", 'solution': '关键信息：鞋子，原价$80，20%折扣，实付$64，刷卡。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '听到 "Can I help you?" 最合适的回答是？', 'options': ["I'm looking for a shirt", 'No problem', 'See you later', 'Thank you'], 'answer': "I'm looking for a shirt"}, {'question': '听到 "It\'s $100 but today it\'s half price." How much does it cost today?', 'options': ['$50', '$100', '$150', '$200'], 'answer': '$50'}, {'question': '听到 "Cash or card?" 这句话出现在什么场景？', 'options': ['结账付款时', '问路时', '上课时', '打电话时'], 'answer': '结账付款时'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '购物对话：价格、尺寸、颜色、支付方式。注意折扣计算和特殊表达。'}]}}, {'title': '旅行对话', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '旅行对话是KET听力的常见话题。学习订票、问路、入住等场景的表达。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '旅行常用表达', 'content': "I'd like to book a ticket to...\nWhat time does the train/plane leave?\nHow long does it take to get to...?\nI have a reservation under the name...\nCan I have a room for two nights?\nWhat time is breakfast served?\nIs there a swimming pool?"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "订票对话：\nA: I'd like to book a train ticket to London, please.\nB: Single or return?\nA: Return, please.\nB: That's £45. The train leaves at 10:15 from Platform 3.\nA: Thank you.", 'solution': '关键信息：伦敦往返票，£45，10:15发车，3号站台。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "入住对话：\nA: Hello, I have a reservation. My name is Smith.\nB: Yes, a double room for three nights.\nA: That's right. What time is breakfast?\nB: From 7 to 10 in the restaurant.\nA: Perfect. Thank you.", 'solution': '关键信息：Smith先生，双人间3晚，早餐7-10点。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '听到 "Single or return?" 是在什么场景？', 'options': ['买火车票', '买衣服', '在餐厅', '在学校'], 'answer': '买火车票'}, {'question': '听到 "The flight is delayed by two hours." 这意味着？', 'options': ['飞机晚点2小时', '飞机提前2小时', '飞行时间2小时', '还有2架飞机'], 'answer': '飞机晚点2小时'}, {'question': '听到 "Breakfast is served from 7 to 10." 什么时候可以吃早餐？', 'options': ['7点到10点', '7点或10点', '7小时', '10小时'], 'answer': '7点到10点'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '旅行对话：订票、时间、站台/登机口、房型、早餐时间。注意single/return的区别。'}]}}, {'title': '学校对话', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '学校生活对话是KET考试的重点话题。涉及课程、作业、活动等。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '学校常用表达', 'content': "What's your favorite subject?\nWhen is the homework due?\nCan you help me with my math?\nThere's a test on Friday.\nThe teacher asked us to read Chapter 3.\nAre you going to the school trip?\nWhat time does the class start?"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "学校对话：\nA: Did you finish the science homework?\nB: Yes, it was about plants. It's due tomorrow.\nA: Can I see yours? I'm stuck on question 3.\nB: Sure. The answer is about photosynthesis.\nA: Thanks! I'll buy you lunch.", 'solution': '关键信息：科学作业，关于植物，明天截止，第3题是关于光合作用。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "学校对话：\nA: There's a school trip to the museum next Friday.\nB: Really? How much does it cost?\nA: It's free! But you need to bring lunch.\nB: Great! I'll sign up today.", 'solution': '关键信息：下周五博物馆之旅，免费，自带午餐。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '听到 "The homework is due on Monday." 这意味着？', 'options': ['作业周一交', '作业周一布置', '周一是周末', '周一没有课'], 'answer': '作业周一交'}, {'question': '听到 "Can you help me with my English homework?" 说话者想要什么？', 'options': ['帮忙做英语作业', '一起玩', '借钱', '买书'], 'answer': '帮忙做英语作业'}, {'question': '听到 "The test has been postponed to next week." 这意味着？', 'options': ['考试推迟到下周', '考试取消了', '考试提前了', '这周考试'], 'answer': '考试推迟到下周'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '学校对话：due date、subject、test/quiz、homework、school trip。注意due和postpone的含义。'}]}}, {'title': '健康与日常对话', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '健康和日常生活的对话也是KET常考话题。掌握看病、运动等表达。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '健康常用表达', 'content': "I don't feel well. / I have a headache/stomachache.\nYou should see a doctor. / Take this medicine.\nHow often should I take it?\nI need to make an appointment.\nI'm allergic to...\nYou should exercise more. / Eat healthy food.\nDrink plenty of water. / Get enough sleep."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "看病对话：\nA: I don't feel well. I have a terrible headache.\nB: How long have you had it?\nA: Since yesterday. And I feel a bit hot.\nB: You should see a doctor. There's one on Main Street.\nA: OK, I'll make an appointment.", 'solution': '关键信息：头痛从昨天开始，有点发烧，建议看医生。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "运动对话：\nA: Do you exercise regularly?\nB: Not really. I just play football sometimes.\nA: You should try swimming. It's great exercise.\nB: That's a good idea. Where can I swim?\nA: There's a pool at the sports center.", 'solution': '关键信息：偶尔踢足球，建议游泳，体育中心有泳池。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '听到 "I have a stomachache." 这个人怎么了？', 'options': ['胃疼', '头疼', '感冒', '发烧'], 'answer': '胃疼'}, {'question': '听到 "Take this medicine three times a day." 怎么吃药？', 'options': ['一天三次', '一次三片', '三天一次', '三小时一次'], 'answer': '一天三次'}, {'question': '听到 "I\'m allergic to peanuts." 这意味着？', 'options': ['对花生过敏', '喜欢吃花生', '花生很贵', '花生很好吃'], 'answer': '对花生过敏'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '健康对话：symptoms (headache, stomachache, fever)、advice (should do...)、medicine (how often)。'}]}}]}, {'name': '口语问答', 'description': 'KET口语考试的问答部分训练', 'sort_order': 3, 'lessons': [{'title': '口语Part 1: 个人信息', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': 'KET口语Part 1是考官问答，关于个人信息。这节课我们练习常见问题和标准回答。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': 'Part 1常见问题', 'content': "What's your name? / How do you spell it?\nWhere are you from?\nHow old are you?\nWhat do you study? / What school do you go to?\nWhat's your favorite subject?\nWhat do you like doing in your free time?\nDo you have any brothers or sisters?"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "考官：What's your favorite subject?\n学生：My favorite subject is science. I like doing experiments and learning about how things work. It's really interesting!", 'solution': '要点：回答完整，不只是"Science." 要加理由。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '考官：What do you like doing in your free time?\n学生：I enjoy reading books and playing basketball. I usually read for an hour before bed. At weekends, I play basketball with my friends.', 'solution': '要点：给出2个爱好并添加细节。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '考官问 "Where are you from?" 最好的回答是？', 'options': ["I'm from Beijing, China. It's a big city.", 'China.', "I don't know.", 'Here.'], 'answer': "I'm from Beijing, China. It's a big city."}, {'question': '考官问 "Do you have any brothers or sisters?" 最好的回答是？', 'options': ["Yes, I have one older sister. She's 18.", 'Yes.', 'No.', 'Maybe.'], 'answer': "Yes, I have one older sister. She's 18."}, {'question': '考官问 "How old are you?" 最好的回答是？', 'options': ["I'm 13 years old.", '13.', 'Old.', 'Young.'], 'answer': "I'm 13 years old."}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '口语Part 1：听清问题→完整回答→添加1-2句细节→保持微笑和眼神交流。'}]}}, {'title': '口语Part 2: 互动对话', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': 'KET口语Part 2是与搭档讨论一个话题。需要表达观点、询问意见和达成一致。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': 'Part 2技巧', 'content': "表达意见：I think... / In my opinion... / I believe...\n同意：I agree. / That's right. / Good idea!\n不同意：I'm not sure about that. / I think... is better.\n询问：What do you think? / Do you agree? / Which one do you prefer?\n建议：Why don't we...? / How about...? / Let's choose..."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "话题：选择生日礼物。选项：书、音乐CD、电影票、运动装备\n学生A: I think a book is a good present. What do you think?\n学生B: Hmm, I'm not sure. She likes music. Why don't we get her a CD?\n学生A: That's a great idea! She loves pop music.\n学生B: Perfect! Let's choose a pop music CD.", 'solution': '要点：表达意见→询问对方→达成一致。有来有往。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': "话题：选择周末活动。选项：看电影、去公园、逛博物馆、在家休息\n学生A: What do you want to do this weekend?\n学生B: How about going to the park? The weather should be nice.\n学生A: I agree! We can have a picnic there.\n学生B: Good idea. Let's bring some sandwiches.", 'solution': '要点：提出建议→讨论→达成一致→添加细节。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '表达个人意见应该怎么说？', 'options': ['I think...', "I don't care", 'Whatever', 'No'], 'answer': 'I think...'}, {'question': '询问对方意见应该怎么说？', 'options': ['What do you think?', 'Tell me now', 'You must agree', "I'm right"], 'answer': 'What do you think?'}, {'question': '表示同意应该怎么说？', 'options': ['I agree. / Good idea!', 'No', 'Maybe', "I don't know"], 'answer': 'I agree. / Good idea!'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': 'Part 2互动：表达意见→询问对方→回应→达成一致。用完整句子，积极互动。'}]}}, {'title': '口语评分标准', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '了解评分标准可以帮你更有针对性地提升口语分数。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': 'KET口语评分', 'content': '语法和词汇（Grammar and Vocabulary）：使用正确的语法和适当的词汇\n发音（Pronunciation）：单词和句子的发音清晰可懂\n互动（Interactive Communication）：与搭档交流的能力\n全局表现（Global Achievement）：整体表现\n\n关键：不需要完美！只要能交流、能理解、能回应就是好成绩。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '5分水平（满分5分）：\n"My favorite subject is science because I enjoy doing experiments. The teacher is really nice too. Last week, we made a volcano model and it was amazing!"', 'solution': '特点：语法正确、词汇丰富、回答详细、有个人经历。'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '3分水平（中等）：\n"I like science. It is interesting. We do experiments."', 'solution': '特点：语法基本正确、词汇简单、回答较短。可以改进但能交流。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '口语考试中，最重要的是？', 'options': ['能够有效交流', '发音像母语者', '用很长的句子', '语速很快'], 'answer': '能够有效交流'}, {'question': '下面哪个回答更好？', 'options': ["I like basketball because it's exciting and I play with my friends every weekend.", 'I like basketball.', 'Basketball good.', 'Play basketball.'], 'answer': "I like basketball because it's exciting and I play with my friends every weekend."}, {'question': '口语Part 2中，如果搭档说的你不同意，应该？', 'options': ['礼貌表达不同意见并给出理由', '说"你错了"', '不说话', '直接走开'], 'answer': '礼貌表达不同意见并给出理由'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '口语评分：交流优先、语法词汇适当、发音清晰、积极互动。不需要完美，自信表达！'}]}}, {'title': '口语模拟练习', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '综合模拟练习，涵盖Part 1和Part 2的所有技巧。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '模拟练习策略', 'content': '① 深呼吸放松\n② 认真听考官和搭档的话\n③ 用完整句子回答\n④ 遇到不会的词用简单词替代\n⑤ 不确定时说 "Could you repeat that?"'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '模拟Part 1：\n考官：Can you tell me about your family?\n学生：Yes! I live with my parents and my younger sister. My father is a doctor and my mother is a teacher. My sister is 8 years old. We often play games together on weekends.', 'solution': '评价：完整回答，有细节，语法正确，词汇适当。很好的回答！'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '模拟Part 2：话题-选择郊游地点\nA: Which place should we visit? The museum or the park?\nB: I think the park is better because the weather is sunny today. What about you?\nA: I agree. We can play games and have a picnic.\nB: Great! Should we bring sandwiches?\nA: Yes! And some fruit too.', 'solution': '评价：有来有往，表达意见，询问对方，达成一致。'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '考官问 "Tell me about your hobbies." 好的回答应该？', 'options': ['说2-3个爱好并添加细节', '只说一个词', '不回答', '反问考官'], 'answer': '说2-3个爱好并添加细节'}, {'question': '搭档说 "I think we should go swimming." 你想去爬山，应该说？', 'options': ["That's nice, but I'd prefer hiking. What do you think?", "No, you're wrong.", 'OK, swimming is fine.', "I don't want to go."], 'answer': "That's nice, but I'd prefer hiking. What do you think?"}, {'question': '没听清考官问题应该？', 'options': ['Could you repeat that, please?', 'Yes.', 'No.', '假装听懂了'], 'answer': 'Could you repeat that, please?'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '口语模拟：放松→认真听→完整回答→积极互动→自信表达！'}]}}]}, {'name': '图片描述与互动', 'description': 'KET口语图片描述和自由讨论训练', 'sort_order': 4, 'lessons': [{'title': '图片描述技巧', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 1, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '描述图片是口语考试的重要部分。学会有系统地描述图片可以拿高分。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '图片描述四步法', 'content': '第一步（总体）：This picture shows...\n第二步（位置）：In the foreground/background, I can see... On the left/right...\n第三步（细节）：The people are...ing. There is/are...\n第四步（推测）：I think they are probably... It looks like...\n\n常用动词：standing, sitting, walking, running, eating, playing, talking, reading, studying'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '描述一张公园图片：人们在公园里做各种活动', 'solution': "This picture shows a park on a sunny day. In the foreground, I can see children playing on the swings. On the right, a family is having a picnic. In the background, some people are walking their dogs. I think it's probably a weekend because there are many people."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '描述一张教室图片', 'solution': "This picture shows a classroom. There are about twenty students sitting at desks. The teacher is standing at the front and writing on the board. Some students are raising their hands. They look interested and engaged. I think they're having a math lesson."}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '图片描述的第一步应该是？', 'options': ['总体描述图片', '描述细节', '猜测内容', '评价图片'], 'answer': '总体描述图片'}, {'question': '描述图片中人物在做什么是用什么时态？', 'options': ['现在进行时 (is/are + doing)', '过去时', '将来时', '现在完成时'], 'answer': '现在进行时 (is/are + doing)'}, {'question': '描述图片中某物的位置用什么句型？', 'options': ['There is/are... / I can see...', 'I want...', 'I had...', 'I will...'], 'answer': 'There is/are... / I can see...'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '图片描述四步：总体→位置→细节→推测。用现在进行时描述动作。'}]}}, {'title': '描述人物与场景', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 2, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '学会描述图片中的人物外貌、穿着和场景细节。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '人物描述词汇', 'content': '年龄：young, old, teenager, child, adult\n外貌：tall, short, thin, with long/short hair\n穿着：wearing a blue T-shirt, jeans, glasses\n表情：smiling, laughing, looking happy/surprised/worried\n动作：reading a book, talking on the phone, carrying a bag\n关系：friends, family, classmates, teacher and student'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '描述图中人物：一个女孩在图书馆', 'solution': 'In the picture, I can see a teenage girl. She has long brown hair and is wearing glasses and a green sweater. She is sitting at a desk in the library and reading a book carefully. She looks very focused.'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '描述图中场景：一个繁忙的街道', 'solution': "This picture shows a busy street in a city. There are many cars and buses on the road. People are walking quickly on the sidewalk. I can see shops and restaurants on both sides. It looks like it's rush hour."}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '描述人物穿着用什么词？', 'options': ['wearing', 'having', 'doing', 'going'], 'answer': 'wearing'}, {'question': '描述人物表情"smiling"说明？', 'options': ['心情好', '生气', '难过', '害怕'], 'answer': '心情好'}, {'question': '描述繁忙场景可以用什么形容词？', 'options': ['busy', 'quiet', 'empty', 'dark'], 'answer': 'busy'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '人物描述：年龄+外貌+穿着+动作+表情。场景描述：什么地方+有什么+感觉怎样。'}]}}, {'title': '对比与讨论', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 3, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '在口语Part 2中，有时需要对比两张图片或讨论选择。这需要比较和讨论的能力。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '对比表达', 'content': "比较相同：Both pictures show... / They both have...\n比较不同：In the first picture..., but in the second...\n偏好表达：I prefer... because... / I'd rather... / I like... more\n连接词：however, although, while, on the other hand"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '对比两张图片：室内活动 vs 室外活动', 'solution': "Both pictures show people having fun. In the first picture, people are playing video games indoors. In the second picture, children are playing football outside. I prefer outdoor activities because they're healthier and more social."}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '讨论选择：看电影在家还是去电影院', 'solution': "I think watching a movie at home is more comfortable. You can sit on your sofa and eat whatever you want. But going to the cinema is more exciting because of the big screen. I'd prefer the cinema for a new movie."}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '对比两张图片时先说什么？', 'options': ['相同点', '不同点', '我的喜好', '价格'], 'answer': '相同点'}, {'question': '表示偏好用什么句型？', 'options': ['I prefer... because...', 'I hate...', 'You must...', "I don't know"], 'answer': 'I prefer... because...'}, {'question': '"however"的作用是？', 'options': ['表示转折', '表示同意', '表示原因', '表示结果'], 'answer': '表示转折'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '对比讨论：先说相同→再说不同→最后表达偏好。用连接词让表达更流畅。'}]}}, {'title': '口语综合模拟', 'lesson_type': 'interactive', 'estimated_minutes': 25, 'sort_order': 4, 'is_published': True, 'content': {'sections': [{'type': 'introduction', 'content': '最后一课！综合所有口语技巧进行模拟练习，为考试做好充分准备。'}, {'type': 'concept', 'title': '考试日准备', 'content': '① 提前到达考场\n② 深呼吸，保持放松\n③ 微笑，与考官和搭档保持眼神交流\n④ 说话清晰，音量适中\n⑤ 不懂就问，不要装懂\n⑥ 积极参与讨论，但也要给搭档说话的机会\n⑦ 用完整句子回答\n⑧ 遇到不会的词用简单词解释'}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '完整口语考试模拟', 'solution': "Part 1 (5-6分钟):\n考官: What's your name?\n你: My name is [name]. You can call me [nickname].\n考官: Where are you from?\n你: I'm from [city]. It's a beautiful city in China.\n考官: What do you enjoy doing?\n你: I really enjoy playing basketball and reading books.\n\nPart 2 (3-4分钟): 与搭档讨论话题\n你: I think we should choose the museum because it's educational.\n搭档: But the beach is more fun!\n你: That's true. How about we visit the museum in the morning and the beach in the afternoon?\n搭档: Great idea!"}, {'type': 'example', 'problem': '考后反思清单', 'solution': '✓ 我用完整句子回答了吗？\n✓ 我问了搭档的意见吗？\n✓ 我的发音清晰吗？\n✓ 我保持了微笑和自信吗？\n✓ 我有足够的互动吗？'}, {'type': 'practice', 'problems': [{'question': '考试当天最重要的是？', 'options': ['放松和自信', '背很多单词', '说得很快', '不说话'], 'answer': '放松和自信'}, {'question': '搭档说话时你应该？', 'options': ['认真听并回应', '看手机', '想自己的答案', '打断对方'], 'answer': '认真听并回应'}, {'question': '遇到不会的词应该？', 'options': ['用简单的词解释或跳过', '停下来不说话', '说中文', '哭'], 'answer': '用简单的词解释或跳过'}]}, {'type': 'summary', 'content': '恭喜完成KET课程！口语考试秘诀：自信、互动、完整回答、享受交流的过程！Good luck! 🎉'}]}}]}]
